---
title: Italian Polpetti Soup with Fresh Pasta and Basil
description: Polpetti is simply the Italian word for meatballs - generally made with beef or veal. We've jazzed up our recipe with Parmesan, herby basil, and a kick of chili to tickle your taste buds!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/italian-polpetti-soup-99f99803.jpg
